查理向克莱尔保证，自己一定会平安回来，然后与她吻别，并且把戒指留在亚伦的摇篮里，再和德斯蒙德一起朝达摩计划水下工作站“窥镜”出发。到达窥镜旁边后，查理用船桨把德斯蒙德打晕，然后独自潜下水。潜入工作站后，葛丽泰（拉娜·帕瑞娅饰）和邦妮（特雷西·米登道夫饰）两名“其他人”出现，并且用枪指住查理。<ref>{{cite episode | credits = Cuse, Carlton (writer) & Lindelof, Damon (writer) & [[傑克·本德|Bender, Jack]] (director) | title = Through the Looking Glass | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 22 | season = 3}}</ref>

== 制作 ==
岛上大部分镜头都是在2007年4月9至12日间拍摄<ref>{{cite web | author = Perez, Mario | date = 2007-04-09 | url = http://gallery.lost-media.com/displayimage.php?pid=102661&fullsize=1 | title = Mira Furlan Guest Stars in "Greatest Hits" | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | accessdate = 2012-10-02 | archivedate = 2012-10-02 | format = JPG | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121002102952/http://gallery.lost-media.com/displayimage.php?pid=102661&fullsize=1}}图像另存为→鼠标右键点击保存的文件→属性→摘要→高级→相片拍照日期</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = Perez, Mario | date = 2007-04-12 | url = http://gallery.lost-media.com/displayimage.php?pid=99738&fullsize=1 | title = Dominic Monaghan Stars in "Greatest Hits" | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | accessdate = 2015-07-13 | archivedate = 2015-07-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150713122948/http://gallery.lost-media.com/displayimage.php?pid=99738&fullsize=1 | deadurl = yes}}图像另存为→鼠标右键点击保存的文件→属性→摘要→高级→相片拍照日期</ref>。节目在电视上首播前，互联网上就出现了详细的剧情介绍<ref>{{cite web | author = Lachonis, Jon | date = 2007-05-20 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-when-spoilers-attack-6709.aspx | title = LOST - When Spoilers Attack! | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150713063045/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-when-spoilers-attack-6709.aspx | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2015-07-13 | publisher = ''BuddyTV'' | accessdate = 2015-09-02 }}</ref>，[[沃尔特·迪斯尼公司|沃尔特·迪斯尼公司]]对此展开调查<ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | title = Ask Ausiello – Does ABC know how the rattlesnake leaked? | work = ''TV Guide'' | publisher = CBS Interactive | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2007-05-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021172857/http://www.tvguide.com/news/does-abc-know-30727.aspx | deadurl = no | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/does-abc-know-30727/ | archivedate = 2012-10-21}}</ref>。节目中达摩计划工作站的名字“窥镜”暗指[[路易斯·卡罗|路易斯·卡罗]]的小说《[[爱丽丝镜中奇遇|爱丽丝镜中奇遇]]》<ref>{{cite web | author1 = Lindelof, Damon | author2 = Cuse, Carlton | date = 2007-05-21 | accessdate = 2009-08-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090811055443/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/index?pn=podcast#t=3421 | archivedate = 2009-08-11 | url = http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/index?pn=podcast#t=3421 | title = The Official ''Lost'' Audio Podcast | publisher = ''American Broadcasting Company''}}</ref>。受[[莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥|莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥]]在《[[泰坦尼克号_(1997年电影)|泰坦尼克号]]》水下表演镜头的启发，多米尼克·莫纳汉在拍摄水下镜头时一度短暂张开嘴，这样可以让观众产生他的确要支持不住了的感觉<ref name="location">{{cite video | title = ''Lost'': On Location – Greatest Hits, in ''Lost: The Complete Third Season – The Unexplored Experience'' | publisher = Buena Vista Home Entertainment | medium = DVD Featurette, disc 7 | date = 2007-12-11}}</ref>。

德斯蒙德曾在第3季之前的剧集中预言，查理肯定会死，《精选辑》就是完结这一预言的开始<ref>{{cite episode | credits = Lindelof, Damon (writer) & Goddard, Drew (writer) & Bender, Jack (director) | title = Flashes Before Your Eyes | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 8 | season = 3}}</ref>，并且会在第3季[[透过窥镜|最终集]]完结<ref>{{cite news | last = Snierson | first = Dan | date = 2007-05-18 | title = Spotlight on Dominic Monaghan | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150411001248/http://www.ew.com/article/2007/05/18/spotlight-dominic-monaghan | deadurl = no | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2007/05/18/spotlight-dominic-monaghan | work = ''[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]'' | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | archivedate = 2015-04-11}}</ref>。拍摄[[迷失_(第二季)|第2季]]第22集《[[致命的3分钟|致命的3分钟]]》（{{lang|en|''Three Minutes''}}）时，众编剧集思广益，为查理发展新的故事情节，上述剧情就由此诞生<ref>{{cite episode | credits = Kitsis, Edward (writer) & Adam Horowitz (writer) & Williams, Stephen (director) | title = Three Minutes | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 22 | season = 2 | date= 2006-05-17}}</ref>。德斯蒙德有通过脑中闪过的画面预测任何人未来的能力<ref>{{cite web | last = Snierson | first = Dan | date = 2007-05-24 | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2007/05/24/lost-dominic-monaghan-charlies-fate | title = The Q&A: Sorry, Charlie | work = ''Entertainment Weekly'' | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150410224726/http://www.ew.com/article/2007/05/24/lost-dominic-monaghan-charlies-fate | archivedate = 2015-04-10}}</ref>，而编剧们之所以选择让查理死去，而不是某个相对而言不太重要的角色，主要是为了让剧情更有吸引力<ref>{{cite web | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2007-05-23 | url = http://community.tvguide.com/blog-entry/TVGuide-Editors-Blog/Ausiello-Report/Lost-Exec-Nights/800015786?start=225& | title = Ausiello Report – Lost Exec on Last Night's Big Death: "It Was Painful" | publisher = ''TV Guide'' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070707215534/http://community.tvguide.com/blog-entry/TVGuide-Editors-Blog/Ausiello-Report/Lost-Exec-Nights/800015786?start=225& | accessdate = 2007-07-07 | archivedate = 2007-07-07 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。此外，编剧们还觉得这样可以很好地展现出查理英勇的一面，让他成为剧中唯一甘愿赴死的角色<ref>{{cite web | last = Veitch | first = Kristin | date = 2007-05-23 | title = Damon Lindelof Breaks 'Radio Silence' to Reveal Why Charlie Died and More | publisher = ''E!'' | accessdate = 2008-06-30 | archivedate = 2008-06-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080630083706/http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=9c9aafc1-e118-4d0c-9686-6b982fbd4e87 | url = http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=9c9aafc1-e118-4d0c-9686-6b982fbd4e87}}</ref>。查理的生命中存在很多问题，但编剧们认为他一直心存良善，所以希望能展现出角色一生中最快乐的时光<ref name="location" />。莫纳汉觉得，《精选辑》可以让观众长时间关注查理一角，做好面对其最终命运的准备<ref>{{cite web | last = Malcolm | first = Shawna | date = 2007-05-24 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/sorry-charlie-lost-35854.aspx | title = Sorry, Charlie: ''Lost'' Star Wanted to "Die" a Hero | work = ''TV Guide'' | publisher = CBS Interactive | accessdate = 2014-11-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141104215807/http://www.tvguide.com/news/sorry-charlie-lost-35854.aspx | archivedate = 2014-11-04 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

《精选辑》是[[露丝·韩德森|露丝·纳德勒]]和柏纳·纳德勒夫妇自第2季后期以来首次在《迷失》中露面<ref>{{cite episode | credits = Lindelof, Damon (writer), Cuse, Carlton (writer) & Bender, Jack (director) | title = Live Together, Die Alone | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 24 | season = 2 | airdate = 2006-05-24}}</ref>，剧-{迷}-们也很高兴看到[[常设角色|两人回归]]<ref name="zap">{{cite web | last = Porter | first = Rick | date = 2007-05-16 | archivedate = 2009-01-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090109025838/http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2007/05/lost_about_a_bo.html | url = http://zap2it.com/2007/05/lost-about-a-boy/ | title = 'Lost': About a boy | work = ''Zap2it'' | publisher = Zap2it/Tribune Broadcasting | accessdate = 2015-09-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。据编剧们介绍，两位演员都需要参与其它项目，所以很长时间没有出现。此外，由于《迷失》中有多位主要演员在第3季早期剧集中出场时间都很有限，所以剧组也担心如果再让两人出镜，可能会招来剧-{迷}-们的不满。<ref>{{cite news | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2007-01-29 | title = Ausiello on ''Scrubs'' | work = ''TV Guide'' | publisher = CBS Interactive}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Martin | first = Ed | date = 2007-01-31 | url = https://www.mediavillage.com/jmentr/2007/01/31/jmer-lost-01-31-07 | title = Exclusive Interview! ''Lost'' Executive Producers Damon Lindelof and Carlton Cuse | work = ''MediaVillage'' | publisher = MyersBizNet | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090201074538/http://www.mediavillage.com/jmentr/2007/01/31/jmer-lost-01-31-07/ | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2009-02-01 | accessdate = 2009-02-01}}</ref>编剧们还认为，如果两人要在节目中亮相，就一定要有和他们有关的情节，而不只是毫无意义地出现在镜头里，他们希望夫妻俩都有能够引起观众兴趣的剧情<ref>{{cite web | author1 = Cuse, Carlton | author2 = Kitsis, Eddie | author3 = Horowitz, Adam | date = 2007-05-30 | url = http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/index?pn=podcast#t=3421 | title = The Official ''Lost'' Audio Podcast | publisher = ''American Broadcasting Company'' | archivedate = 2009-08-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090811055443/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/index?pn=podcast#t=3421 | accessdate = 2009-08-11}}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
[[File:Dominic_Monaghan_2003.jpg|thumb]]

《精选辑》于2007年5月16日通过[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]首播，播出期间平均吸引了1232万美国观众收看，在该周美国播映的所有电视剧中排名第15<ref>{{cite web | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=052207_06 | title = Weekly Program Rankings From 05/14/07 Through 05/20/07 | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | archivedate = 2014-11-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141106163041/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=052207_06 | publisher = American Broadcasting Company | accessdate = 2014-11-06 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>，与之前同时段播出的《迷失》剧集收视情况基本相同<ref>{{cite news | last = Sullivan | first = Brian Ford | date = 2007-09-10 | title = The Ten Things You Need to Know About the New Season | work = ''The Futon Critic''}}</ref>。节目的前半集有1190万美国观众收看，后半集则增至1280万<ref>{{cite web | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=052207_05 | title = Weekly Primetime Ratings Wrap-Up From 05/14/07 Through 05/20/07 | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | publisher = American Broadcasting Company | accessdate = 2012-02-10 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-02-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210142957/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=052207_05}}</ref>。剧集在18至49岁年龄段观众群中取得的收视率为5.2/14，这意味着全美所有该年龄段人群里有5.4%观看节目首播，而当时有看电视的该年龄段观众群中则有14%选择收看《精选辑》，在当晚所有预定剧情电视节目中排在首位。《精选辑》还于同一天晚上通过[[CTV电视网|CTV电视网]]在加拿大首播，有87万5000人观看，在该周所有电视节目里排第27位<ref>{{cite report | work = ''BBM Canada'' | date = 2007-05-20 | url = http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat05142007.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090318143127/http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat05142007.pdf | archivedate = 2009-03-18 | title = Top Programs – Total Canada (English) | accessdate = 2009-03-18 | deadurl = yes | format = PDF}}</ref>。节目在英国播出时吸引了121万观众，是该周英国所有非地面电视台播出节目的收视亚军，仅次于《[[凯蒂和彼得：新篇章|凯蒂和彼得：新篇章]]》（{{lang|en|''Katie & Peter: The Next Chapter''}}）<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2009-05-23 | deadurl = yes | url = http://gallifreyone.com/news-archives.php?id=5-2007 | date = 2007-05-30 | accessdate = 2009-05-23 | title = 42 - Final Ratings | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090523083537/http://www.gallifreyone.com/news-archives.php?id=5-2007 | work = ''Outpost Gallifrey''}}</ref>。澳大利亚则有1001万观众收看《精选辑》，在该周排名第51位<ref>{{cite web|last=Dale |first=David |date=2007-07-21 |url=http://blogs.smh.com.au/sit/archives/2007/07/next_ratings_race.html |title=Stay in Touch – The Ratings Race: Week 29 |publisher=''The Sydney Morning Herald'' |accessdate=2015-09-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120424094302/http://blogs.smh.com.au/sit/archives/2007/07/next_ratings_race.html |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-04-24 }}</ref>。

《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的帕特里克·戴（{{lang|en|Patrick Day}}）认为，考虑到这是在第3季的倒数第2集，要为本季大结局做准备，《精选辑》在很多方面都比其他剧集要优异得多。他很高兴杰克一角不再像之前那么无趣，也很高兴露丝·纳德勒和柏纳·纳德勒夫妇回归，并且称赞节目中采用[[迈克·吉亚奇诺|迈克·吉亚奇诺]]创作、以鼓点为主的配乐。<ref>{{cite news | last = Day | first = Patrick | date = 2007-05-17 | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2007/05/lost_counting_d.html | title = 'Lost': Counting down... | work = ''Los Angeles Times'' | accessdate = 2015-09-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120225043648/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2007/05/lost_counting_d.html | archivedate = 2012-02-25}}</ref>杰夫·约翰逊（{{lang|en|Jeff Jensen}}）在《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》发文，称赞莫纳汉通过本集中给出他在《迷失》中最出色的一场演出<ref>{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff "Doc" |date=2007-05-17 |accessdate=2015-09-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609151334/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20039187_2%2C00.html |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-06-09 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20039187_2,00.html |title=The "Greatest Hits" of Charlie's Life |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' }}</ref>，还觉得节目最后一幕“扣人心弦”<ref>{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff "Doc" |date=2007-05-17 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20039187,00.html |title=Hit Lists |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130130182327/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20039187%2C00.html |deadurl=yes |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2013-01-30 |archivedate=2013-01-30 }}</ref>，其[[特殊效果|特技效果]]令人惊叹，值得[[黄金时段艾美奖|艾美奖]]肯定<ref>{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff "Doc" |date=2007-05-17 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20039187_3,00.html |title=Charlie Risks His Life |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609151359/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20039187_3%2C00.html |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-06-09 |accessdate=2012-06-09 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[E!|E!]]}}频道的[[克里斯汀·多斯·桑托斯|克里斯汀·维奇]]（{{lang|en|Kristin Veitch}}）同样称赞莫纳汉的演出，称《精选辑》是《迷失》高品质的典范之作<ref>{{cite news | author1 = Veitch, Kristin | author2 = Godwin, Jennifer | date = 2007-05-17 | work = ''E!'' | title = It's Charlie's Waterworld, We Just Live in It | accessdate = 2015-09-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110629161008/http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/b3689__amp_amp_lt_i_amp_amp_gt_Lost_amp_amp_lt__i_amp_amp_gt__Redux__It_s_Charlie_s_Waterworld__We_Just_Live_in_It.html | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/b3689__amp_amp_lt_i_amp_amp_gt_Lost_amp_amp_lt__i_amp_amp_gt__Redux__It_s_Charlie_s_Waterworld__We_Just_Live_in_It.html | archivedate = 2011-06-29}}</ref>。《[[圣荷西信使报|圣荷西信使报]]》的查理·麦科勒姆（{{lang|en|Charlie McCollum}}）称，《迷失》第3季的后几集就像“一场绝对的惊悚之旅”<ref>{{cite news | last = McCollum | first = Charlie | date = 2007-12-31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120825021549/http://www.mercurynews.com/charliemccollum/ci_7850755?nclick_check=1 | url = http://www.mercurynews.com/charliemccollum/ci_7850755?nclick_check=1 | title = TV's Top 25 | work = ''San Jose Mercury News'' | accessdate = 2015-09-03 | archivedate = 2012-08-25}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}网站的克里斯·卡拉波特（{{lang|en|Chris Carabott}}）给予本集的评分为8.5（最高10分），称赞剧中杰克和查理两个角色的发展，以及本的扮演者爱默生的表演功底<ref>{{cite web | last = Carabott | first = Chris | date = 2007-05-17 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/05/17/lost-greatest-hits-review | title = "Greatest Hits" Review | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140925121030/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/05/17/lost-greatest-hits-review | deadurl = no | work = ''IGN'' | accessdate = 2015-09-03 | archivedate = 2014-09-25}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[TWoP|TWoP]]}}网站的露露·贝茨（{{lang|en|Lulu Bates}}）对节目的评级为{{lang|en|A}}–（最高{{lang|en|A}}+）<ref>{{cite web | last = Bates | first = Lulu | title = Footprints | work = ''Television Without Pity'' | accessdate = 2012-02-07 | date = 2007-05-21 | url = http://www.televisionwithoutpity.com/Shows/Lost/Stories/Greatest-Hits | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120207163253/http://www.televisionwithoutpity.com/Shows/Lost/Stories/Greatest-Hits | archivedate = 2012-02-07}}</ref>。《[[美国在线|美国在线]]》电视小队的艾琳·马特尔（{{lang|en|Erin Martell}}）给《精选辑》打出的分数为6（最高为7），称赞节目成功建立起季终集的声势，但也指出剧情中查理的游泳能力存在前后矛盾的地方<ref>{{cite web | last = Martell | first = Erin | date = 2007-05-17 | url = http://www.tvsquad.com/2007/05/17/lost-greatest-hits | title = Lost: Greatest Hits | work = ''TV Squad'' | accessdate = 2011-05-21 | archivedate = 2011-05-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110521145215/http://www.tvsquad.com/2007/05/17/lost-greatest-hits/}}</ref>。斯科特·朱巴（{{lang|en|Scott Juba}}）认为，《精选辑》是第3季最出众的一集，称其中的闪回镜头激起观众内心的人类情感认同，正是这种认同成就了《迷失》的成功。这部电视剧真正了不起的地方不在其情节的曲折或神秘，而在于它能让观众对角色感同身受，进而激发出几乎任何人都会认同的主题。<ref>{{cite web | last = Juba | first = Scott | date = 2007-12-11 | url = http://www.the-trades.com/article.php?id=6116 | title = DVD Review: ''Lost: The Complete Third Season'' | work = ''The Trades'' | accessdate = 2012-02-07 | archivedate = 2012-02-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120207193200/http://www.the-trades.com/article.php?id=6116}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[BuddyTV|BuddyTV]]}}网站的乔恩·拉索尼斯（{{lang|en|Jon Lachonis}}）指出，本集在将查理转变成讨人喜欢的角色方面获得了极大成功<ref>{{cite web | last = Lachonis | first = Jon "DocArzt" | date = 2007-05-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120111130937/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-322-greatest-hits-recap-6541.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-322-greatest-hits-recap-6541.aspx | title = 3.21 'Greatest Hits' Recap | work = ''BuddyTV'' | accessdate = 2012-01-11 | archivedate = 2012-01-11 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

《精选辑》播出后参与了[[第59届艾美奖|第59届]][[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]][[黄金时段艾美奖剧情类电视剧杰出导演奖|杰出导演]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Lachonis |first=Jon "DocArzt" |date=2007-06-29 |title=''Lost'' Producers Look "Through the Looking Glass" for Emmy Glory |url=http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-producers-look-through-th-7109.aspx |work=''BuddyTV'' |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015-09-03 |archivedate=2012-01-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111130102/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-producers-look-through-th-7109.aspx }}</ref>和[[黄金时段艾美奖剧情类电视剧杰出编剧奖|杰出编剧奖]]角逐<ref>{{cite web | author = Boomer | date = 2007-07-26 | url = http://goldderbyforums.latimes.com/eve/forums/a/tpc/f/1106078764/m/53610293 | accessdate = 2007-10-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071009230644/http://goldderbyforums.latimes.com/eve/forums/a/tpc/f/1106078764/m/53610293 | title = 2007 Emmys Confirmed Episode Submissions | work = ''Los Angeles Times Envelope'' | archivedate = 2007-10-09 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>，还获得金卷轴奖最佳电视音效剪辑奖提名<ref>{{cite web | work = Motion Picture Sound Editors | date = 2008-02-05 | url = http://www.mpse.org/goldenreels/2008awards/2008tvnominees.html | title = 2008 Golden Reel Award Nominees: Television | accessdate = 2013-06-07 | archivedate = 2013-06-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130607160139/http://www.mpse.org/goldenreels/2008awards/2008tvnominees.html}}</ref>。

